    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So here's an update of why it's working on my side and not on yours: it's working only if you are using React InstantSearch in an uncontrolled mode. Because you're using the `searchState` and `onSearchStateChange` props, then you are in controlled mode, and this tricks can't work.\r\n\r\nI keep you updated about the development of a solution for this use case. ",
